Torpedo Moscow beat Arsenal Tula 3-1 in the Russian Premier League on Sunday . 
  Torpedo fans displayed a flag with a Nazi symbol during the game . 
  Club must play two home games in an empty stadium . 
  Club have already been punished for monkey chants at Zenit St Petersburg . 
  Sunday's game was the club's fourth racism-related punishment this season . 
  The club must play their next two games behind closed doors . 
 